race.description: Magain Fielke Real Estate Gawler Plate (C1)
race.comment: ANNANDA (5) stepped up to the middle distance and broke her maiden at Strathalbyn. Was heavily supported, and she can take the next step for the Stokes yard. FIORA BLUE (8) just missed in the same contest, also up in trip and hits this at peak. Can threaten again with average luck in the run. Tougher sorting the rest. TAKEN ON FAITH (9) was in the market against the above pair but settled back and didn't finish it off. Has a handy 3kg claim today and she would get some of the money purse if she put her best foot forward. DERBY DOWNS (2) should be better for his first run over a middle distance. Maps well and is locally trained.
